The paper discusses the use of Distributed Certificate Authorities (DCA) in wireless and ad hoc networks, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses different types of DCA protocols, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper proposes the best DCA security services in terms of performance and level of security, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
